.TH CYGNUS-FM 0.8-6 "March 2026" "Version 0.8-6" "Cygnus File Manager"
.SH NAME
cygnus-fm \- minimalist file manager for Cygnus WM

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B cygnus-fm
[\fIDIR\fR]

.SH DESCRIPTION
.B cygnus-fm
is a minimalist file manager written for the Cygnus Window Manager. It features dual pane (sidebar), icon support, and basic file operations (copy, cut, paste).

.SH KEY BINDINGS
.TP
.B Up/Down Arrows
Navigate the file list.
.TP
.B Return
Open the selected file or directory.
.TP
.B Backspace
Go to the parent directory.
.TP
.B Ctrl+c
Copy selected file.
.TP
.B Ctrl+x
Cut selected file.
.TP
.B Ctrl+v
Paste from clipboard.
.TP
.B Ctrl+h
Toggle hidden files.
.TP
.B q, Escape
Exit the file manager.

.SH FILES
.TP
.I ~/.cygnus-wm/icons
Configuration file for the icon theme.

